{"tid":881109,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［狗鐵縮骨史］每月之星抽獎 2月咁啱抽中29號","createTime":"2018-10-29T07:43:04.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-29T13:54:44.000Z","uid":136994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"77ca2414ffe027359faa9dadc690ad09b0e7f4e8","tid":881109,"uid":136994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T07:43:04.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/daily/article/20170124/19907144\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20170124%2F19907144&d=7329xsprZlMi8AYOta0tnKS6uTmBE%2FuUnOR61Sj848o%3D&h=8c5815bf\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20170124%2F19907144&h=128e4917\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/daily/article/20170124/19907144</a><br />\n<br />\n話說港鐵（066）每個月都會抽出每月「生日之星」，抽出一個日子，咁呢日生日嘅朋友，就可以有生日獎！<br />\n<br />\n昨日港鐵就搵埋主席馬時亨、黃秋生、泳兒、湯怡去抽2月生日獎！結果係邊日呢，登登登登！就係每四年先出現一次嘅2月29日！<br />\n<br />\n對港鐵來講，抽中呢一日應該會慳咗錢，四年一遇嘅一日，呢日生日嘅人數，點計都少一截啩！對於呢一日生日嘅朋友來講，雖然今年連2月29日都冇，但因為港鐵，今年應該會多一種「沒有被忘記」嘅感覺。<br />\n<br />\n對上一次出現2月29日，其實就係上年。好多人或者會問，到底2月29日出世，法律上閏年以外年份，邊日先當係生日。本人上網一Search，根據《成年歲數（有關條文）條例》，喺閏年以外嘅其他年份，係以3月1日作為佢嘅生日，真係長知識了。其實呢，如果你呢日生日，都仲有啲嘢係著數過人嘅，好似海洋公園生日免費入場優惠咁，你可以揀喺2月28日或3月1日是但一日入場。<br />\n<br />\n港鐵「開心搭‧生日獎」的生日之星可獲贈生日獎乙份,每份生日獎包括一張特別設計的「Happy Birthday 全日通」車票、一張50元港鐵商場現金禮券及其它商戶優惠券。<br />\n<br />\n2月29日生日嘅朋友，只須於今年2月1日至28日內任何一個星期日，上午11時至下午6時到大部份港鐵站的特設換領站或客務中心，或於平日到紅磡站的旅客服務中心，憑身份證即可換領生日獎。"},{"pid":"1be00f4b8a508bd8a31bdbc464e571e28062270c","tid":881109,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T07:45:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d43128d1c755df9241491b1132d6058ae876282","tid":881109,"uid":23707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T07:47:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08993d888175fd28f0d9d1332405dd2d7275d62a","tid":881109,"uid":136994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T07:53:02.000Z","msg":"當大家睇到港鐵搞抽獎都咁縮骨，就知道佢一定會揀星期六日半價<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8505e679ea3d5d839d1e517fba6e4e9a28d0b91d","tid":881109,"uid":31780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T08:00:39.000Z","msg":"2017<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5da56ebe4f4c048e30662b07de5e5d3a8cd9530e","tid":881109,"uid":136994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T13:54:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}